Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真是亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,援軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不 他們也是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這都算到了？何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,威巴 你還太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你能逃到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,通訊干擾…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,電子戰也是對方技高一籌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有新客人 立即返回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,逃了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人那邊似乎也有情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,撿回一條命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,比起這個 我更擔心宗介的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,援軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是新敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,扔掉武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然讓目標女人逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不過還有很多問題要審問你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,抓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我想起了溪山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了 雷蒙 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,行動失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:06:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,相良宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.80,note3,,0,0,0,,{\fs52\pos(1095,982)}Laevatein
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,即將投下「烈焰魔劍」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,烈…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,烈焰魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不過這名字也是它自稱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這架機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見 中士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是AL嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不過本機的名稱是ARX-8 烈焰魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,相良中士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,本機申請回歸到你的戰爭中來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,還用問嗎 我允許
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我很榮幸 請先登機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,警報
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,敵軍AS 貝希摩斯型三架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,以及柯達爾型三架正在逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要先大鬧一場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,行 我們上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼功率
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,本機尚未進行過正規的試駕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 那玩意能用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,λ-Driver嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 因為沒用過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,算了不管了 試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,成功 船到橋頭自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然捏了一把冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,接近警報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,武器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,請保持住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,還有輔助臂？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,由我來負責控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,推測當前負重約為1500噸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,請立刻脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,還有別的武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,請用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,爆破榴彈炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,165毫米口徑!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,威力和後坐力也超乎尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,必須要配合λ-Driver才能開火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,請多加注意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,強制激發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,成功 擊穿敵機力場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,再來一炮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,還剩誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一架貝希摩斯型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,已經放棄戰鬥 正在撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是否追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這個武器的射程是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不 可行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,爆破榴彈炮轉為加農榴彈炮模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,最大射程為30公里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好 就試它一試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,命中 目標擊毀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,已經脫離危險空域了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好 保持現在的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,往西北偏北方向飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,別做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我是認真的 立刻返航
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到你還挺精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,返航
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我就開槍打他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,反正是個連自己的槍都看不住的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我真的會開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就像剛才對雷納德·泰斯塔羅莎所做的那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有決心開槍的人 是不能拿起槍的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,強迫他人就是在傷害他人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你辦得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我就辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我現在才會站在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也見不到他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,把槍給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 我盡可能答應你的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,讓直升機返航
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這…我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,雷納德需要治療
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還有被敵人擊落的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你先冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,把槍放下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那…讓我和他道別
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,用無線通訊機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 這些都是宗介收拾掉的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真叫人吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是叫烈焰魔劍來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一架可靠的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果當時美利達島上有它在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,待會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 相良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那架機體還是盡量不要讓俘虜看見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,AL 開啟ECS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,進入隱形模式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,本機未搭載ECS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,因為超出常規的功率以及λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒有餘力搭載多餘的電子部件了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,幾乎沒有電子裝備…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是現代戰爭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可以和友軍共享數據
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要洩氣 努力奮進吧 中士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是有多餘的部件麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,應該把你扔進垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,換成ECS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,該提議毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,沒了我 本機只是一坨廢鐵…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,捕捉到新的無線信號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎是在呼叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是否接通？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,接進來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,聽得見嗎 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是千鳥嗎 你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這一路上發生了好多事 也迷茫過很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但我還是來了 我已經來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,為了救出你 帶你回到那所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪裡 快告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 停下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,停下？你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我試圖尋求自由的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就一定會有人受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 就連恭子也發生了那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 你還是忘了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們倆就到此為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,到此為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,還是不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事我絕對不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有人受傷也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我把話說完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我要給你下令了 你聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,無論付出多大的犧牲也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕死幾個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,幾百…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,幾萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,死幾億人也無所謂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你一定要來接我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,用上你所有的 脫離常識的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,給人添麻煩的 亂七八糟的軍事技能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,無論敵人有多厲害 你都要把他打得落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,來到我身邊抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你辦得到吧 說話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會去 你等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介 我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我也愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那下次真正見面的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要和我接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,用盡全力 無論在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我先聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才說的幾億人只是打個比方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哦…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,被你將了一軍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你真的要尋死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒演戲 我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我已經下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真是服了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊說「宗介 我愛你」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊說「我也愛你」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真是聽不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你趕緊去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,早死早超生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,半年不見 就這麼問候我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是成長了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐好欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,總之沒事就好 相良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,待會再和你慢慢聊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,無線我都聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:19:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,為我引見一下你的長官吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然順勢來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不過還是要先交涉一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,長官…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,相良中士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,泰莎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,泰莎妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我想死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,泰莎妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,人家想你想得好苦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這兩人怎麼會在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,說來話長…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我要護理 給我護理一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,別理他 給我護理就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,放手啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,護理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,護理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:21:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,言歸正傳 我向你介紹一下這位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他是DGSE的特工
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙 她就是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是我的上司
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可…這姑娘…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你要介紹給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一見鍾情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,太明顯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,粉絲俱樂部會員又要喜加一了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒有確認他的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,相良中士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你願意回歸我的部隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我申請歸隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:21:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我當然同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.98,0:22:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuatha de Danaan歡迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在歡迎之列嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,泰斯塔羅莎上校
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了 AL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興你也沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 上校
